{"thag3.10:0.1":"Theragatha 3.10 ","thag3.10:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.10:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.10:0.4":"Satimattiyattheragatha ","thag3.10:1.1":"“Ahu tuyham pure saddha, ","thag3.10:1.2":"sa te ajja na vijjati; ","thag3.10:1.3":"Yam tuyham tuyhamevetam, ","thag3.10:1.4":"natthi duccaritam mama. ","thag3.10:2.1":"Anicca hi cala saddha, ","thag3.10:2.2":"evam dittha hi sa maya; ","thag3.10:2.3":"Rajjantipi virajjanti, ","thag3.10:2.4":"tattha kim jiyyate muni. ","thag3.10:3.1":"Paccati munino bhattam, ","thag3.10:3.2":"Thokam thokam kule kule; ","thag3.10:3.3":"Pindikaya carissami, ","thag3.10:3.4":"Atthi janghabalam mama”ti. ","thag3.10:3.5":"… Satimattiyo thero …. "}